On-Screen Display X coordinate
Displays On-Screen Display X coordinate in reference to the origin. Click this field to enter desired position manually or use the adjacent buttons to increase or decrease it. Use On-Screen Display preview window for visual control of On-Screen Display appearance when adjusting the position.

